                          <strong>2022/2023 ADMISSION SCREENING EXERCISE (1ST BATCH)</strong>
                          <p>CENTRE FOR CONTINUING EDUCATION (CCE)<br>INSTITUTE OF PART-TIME STUDIES (IPTS)<br>2022/2023 ADMISSION SCREENING EXERCISE (1ST BATCH)
                          <br> You are hereby invited to attend the screening Exercise(1st Batch) scheduled to hold on Monday 3rd April, 2023 at the Institue of Part-time studies, Ayegbaju Campus by 9am with the following credentials (ORIGINAL COPIES for sightinh and photocopies for submission):
